{% schema %}
  {
    
    "name": "Section 7",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-607393614816870998 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/sheikhashadul/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_ARTICLE&editorId=607381796862034487&sectionId=607393614816870998)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmEobjBzUd_text","label":"ggmEobjBzUd_text","default":"That's Why I Discovered Something Extraordinary When Studying Research From French Scientists Examining Children With Hutchinson-Gilford Syndrome - The \"Benjamin Button\" Disease That Causes Rapid Aging In Children."},{"type":"html","id":"gg26eYpr_Tf_text","label":"gg26eYpr_Tf_text","default":"<p>The medical notes from their 2003 study showed these children shared the same symptoms with adults who looked far beyond their years…</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIa8evHk0o_text","label":"ggIa8evHk0o_text","default":"<p>They had massive levels of an <strong>aging protein.</strong> And this isn’t a protein we eat. It's a protein molecule that builds up in our skin cells called <strong>Progerin</strong>.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGK2GnGpbi_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggGK2GnGpbi_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s6img.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxRky0BdP4_text","label":"ggxRky0BdP4_text","default":"<p>You see, my own research and that of others has shown conclusively that Progerin levels are directly correlated with how quickly our skin ages.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJjHhWrEyv_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggJjHhWrEyv_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s6img.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJO2Nv8YuB_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggJO2Nv8YuB_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s6bx1img.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvQi7ijQ1q_text","label":"ggvQi7ijQ1q_text","default":"<p>In 2012, the <strong>Advances in Dermatology Study </strong>showed that exposure to UVA rays from the sun significantly increases the amount of Progerin in our skin, which explains why excessive tanning prematurely ages us.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggD2H-JZ0tG_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggD2H-JZ0tG_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s6bx1img.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkTyCiukPO_text","label":"ggkTyCiukPO_text","default":"<p>In 2012, the <strong>Advances in Dermatology Study </strong>showed that exposure to UVA rays from the sun significantly increases the amount of Progerin in our skin, which explains why excessive tanning prematurely ages us.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCRPVGVGxQ_text","label":"ggCRPVGVGxQ_text","default":"<p>And in one of the largest clinical studies ever conducted, 23 women ages 34 to 78 were analyzed for their response to anti-Progerin compounds.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggANQF96-3t_text","label":"ggANQF96-3t_text","default":"<p><strong>What the researchers discovered about these women's skin was shocking.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGMWWeDiZm_text","label":"ggGMWWeDiZm_text","default":"<p>Not only did the women's skin become softer, smoother and firmer...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggoK6BJKoyO_text","label":"ggoK6BJKoyO_text","default":"<p>It looked and felt younger and healthier than it had in years.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggr1gtYRUbN_text","label":"ggr1gtYRUbN_text","default":"<p><strong>And because the skin cells were now fully enriched with these anti-Progerin compounds, they had a radiant glow as if they just came back from their honeymoon!</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKC6D9NXwF_text","label":"ggKC6D9NXwF_text","default":"<p>Women who thought they could never get rid of aging skin, jowls, or turkey neck without surgery saw dramatic improvements.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3LqAAKT9R_text","label":"gg3LqAAKT9R_text","default":"<p><strong>A month later they cried tears of joy, experiencing the sensation of skin that is smooth...fresh… and youthful once again.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggi0_JJhhgZ_text","label":"ggi0_JJhhgZ_text","default":"<p>Looking at their transformations, I began to notice something that nobody else had seen:</p>"}],
    "blocks": [{"type": "@app"}],
    "locales": {}
  }
